Class Ngram<T extends Comparable<T> & Serializable>

  • edu.umn.biomedicus.common.grams.Ngram<T>

    Bigram<T>, Trigram<T>

    public class Ngram<T extends Comparable<T> & Serializable>
implements Bigram<T>, Trigram<T>

    An implementation of Bigram and Trigram which uses an subarray.
